ygData.messageBody:
1- 24 is a good level because it's not impossible and you will get decent
exp.
2- If you are saying that you need 6 pairs of jboots, then be prepared to
camp for a full week, 6 to 10 hours per day.
3- Have lots of caffeine handy and things to do/read or you will go insane.
4- You will learn to HATE that room.

Astur il'Ayan, Cleric of Brell
Solusek Ro
